  "text": "Score Generation: Iris matching scores are computed from string iris feature codes extracted by the cumulative-sum-based grey change analysis technique. To verify the similarity of two iris codes, Hamming Distance (HD) based on the matching algorithm [CITATION_1] is used. The smaller the HD, the higher the similarity of the compared iris codes. The HD denotes the iris raw matching score, S iris , which is computed as:",
